body_html:
There are 135 code references on GitHub for the query tf.transpose(tf.gather(tf.transpose, though this includes a lot of repo clones (GitHub search is pretty mediocre).

Internally at Google, there are 48 uses of the workaround.

See also: #9236 (comment)
